{"tid":1676531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[幾乎沒有人到場] 添馬公園集會未獲響應 婆婆：見年輕人被打好心痛","createTime":"2019-10-26T13:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T15:05:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ad4d9ec68f32749f7a803bc26882adf168f563ca","tid":1676531,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R6zAJlVfmpgR0q9JPaQMyw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-hk/hk01_725/1ae8754d24025efd479ea282e734ce3e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FR6zAJlVfmpgR0q9JPaQMyw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fhk01_725%2F1ae8754d24025efd479ea282e734ce3e&h=5fe0f1b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n反修例風波持續，有市民發起於今日（26日）在添馬公園舉行主題為「對抗白色恐怖反極權」集會，聲援因曾參與示威而被企業解僱的員工，但集會未申請不反對通知書。惟直至下午2時，現場仍未見有市民聚集。期間，有數名中、老年人到場稱要參加集會；其中到場的麥婆婆指「見到後生被人打好心痛」，因此連月來都堅持參加集會表達訴求。<br />\n<br />\n早前，有多名國泰、港龍航空職員早前疑因政見問題遭到解僱，再有市民發起今日（26日）下午1時到金鐘添馬公園集會，聲援因政治立場而遭到解僱的員工。惟直至下午1時半，仍未見有市民聚集，場面平靜。<br />\n<br />\n下午1時半，有數名中、老年人到場稱要參加集會。其中一位是今年86歲的麥婆婆，她獨自到場參加集會，惟見到幾乎沒有人到場，大呼「失望」；她直言「見到後生被人打好心痛」，又指「邊個落台都冇用，都係大陸控制我哋」，因此仍會參加今日的其他集會。麥婆婆指，在數月反修例運動中，幾乎每星期都會靠聽收音機，和從子女口中知悉集會消息，參加集會表達訴求。"},{"pid":"b42a4b17c2ad17de8f3c4d1b3ba363117d26a2ae","tid":1676531,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T13:44:28.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7761a43b2893d1989fa994a33c81b82933db49d1","tid":1676531,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:01:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/992Y4gw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F992Y4gw.jpg&h=d4bcf577&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rwKc8Jc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrwKc8Jc.jpg&h=7f03b626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zjAcpgx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzjAcpgx.jpg&h=8a448908&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j2QS8Je.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj2QS8Je.gif&h=ebb2708a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"300fcaa18f892160ed819fbc9cc976963288d852","tid":1676531,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"完全唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7d2c17168d07d86a995c659734d1efcbb028299","tid":1676531,"uid":3406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:04:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9dcf00de663640c3ca40a82966505fbe261586","tid":1676531,"uid":258088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:05:10.000Z","msg":"對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5299a0ade2760504cdada3ddaa0af0c33431fc1d","tid":1676531,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:05:40.000Z","msg":"隔離開左po上左熱門啦，要討論就過去討論啦"},{"pid":"5dfa0b30d4ccfd596a1f7c3bc177dd513b39daa6","tid":1676531,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:06:30.000Z","msg":"好多有心人<br />\n唉<br />\n對不起她們"},{"pid":"840acfacab9b7c6cb020b295c7d338311f27b2ec","tid":1676531,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dfa0b30d4ccfd596a1f7c3bc177dd513b39daa6","tid":1676531,"uid":304160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:06: